{"title":"Potion of degeneration","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Potion_of_degeneration","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.31](/0.31 \"0.31\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n| Type | Potion                                                                                                     |\n| :--- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Name | Potion of Degeneration                                                                                     |\n| Icon | [![Potion of degeneration.png](/images/4/46/Potion_of_degeneration.png)](/File:Potion_of_degeneration.png) |\n\n|   |                                                                         |\n| - | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | A noxious concotion which reduces strength, intelligence and dexterity. |\n\nQuaffing a **potion of degeneration** temporarily reduces each stat ([strength](/Strength \"Strength\"), [dexterity](/Dexterity \"Dexterity\"), and [intelligence](/Intelligence \"Intelligence\")) by 1-3 points. This can be dangerous (although not directly fatal) for [species](/Species \"Species\") with very low stats, since reaching zero or less in a stat will cause [stat zero](/Stat_zero \"Stat zero\") penalties. The lost stats will recover over time as [experience](/Experience \"Experience\") is gained. [Xom](/Xom \"Xom\") is somewhat amused if you quaff an unidentified potion of degeneration, but this is hard to do intentionally.\n\n> There was something very wrong with that liquid!\n\n## History\n\n- Prior to [0.18](/0.18 \"0.18\"), the potion lowered a random stat by 1-4 instead of decreasing every stat by 1-3.\n- Prior to [0.13](/0.13 \"0.13\"), having a stat reduced to 0 could cause [stat death](/Stat_death \"Stat death\"). This was replaced by the [stat zero](/Stat_zero \"Stat zero\") penalties.\n\n| [Potions](/Potion \"Potion\")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |\n| -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| [Ambrosia](/Potion_of_ambrosia \"Potion of ambrosia\") • [