v id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #33FF66; background-color: #e0fae0; border-left: 15px solid #33FF66; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.31\" title=\"0.31\">0.31</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Type\n</th>\n<td> Potion\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Name\n</th>\n<td> Potion of Degeneration\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Icon\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/File:Potion_of_degeneration.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Potion of degeneration.png\" src=\"/images/4/46/Potion_of_degeneration.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>\n</td></tr></table>\n</div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A noxious concotion which reduces strength, intelligence and dexterity.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p>Quaffing a <b>potion of degeneration</b> temporarily reduces each stat (<a href=\"/Strength\" title=\"Strength\">strength</a>, <a href=\"/Dexterity\" title=\"Dexterity\">dexterity</a>, and <a href=\"/Intelligence\" title=\"Intelligence\">intelligence</a>) by 1-3 points. This can be dangerous (although not directly fatal) for <a href=\"/Species\" title=\"Species\">species</a> with very low stats, since reaching zero or less in a stat will cause <a href=\"/Stat_zero\" title=\"Stat zero\">stat zero</a> penalties. The lost stats will recover over time as <a href=\"/Experience\" title=\"Experience\">experience</a> is gained. <a href=\"/Xom\" title=\"Xom\">Xom</a> is somewhat amused if you quaff an unidentified potion of degeneration, but this is hard to do intentionally.\n</p>\n<blockquote style=\"float:none; padding: 10px 15px 10px 15px; display:table; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; background-color: #f9f9f9; color: black; font-size: 95%; margin-top: 1em; margin-right: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1.6em;\">There was something very wrong with that liquid!</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.18\" title=\"0.18\">0.18</a>, the potion lowered a random stat by 1-4 instead of decreasing every stat by 1-3.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.13\" title=\"0.13\">0.13</a>, having a stat reduced to 0 could cause <a href=\"/Stat_death\" title=\"Stat death\">stat death</a>. This was replaced by the <a href=\"/Stat_zero\" title=\"Stat zero\">stat zero</a> penalties.</li></ul>\n<center>\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 65%; font-size: 85%;\">\n\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Potion\" title=\"Potion\">Potions</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td> <a href=\"/Potion_of_ambrosia\" title=\"Potion of ambrosia\">Ambrosia</a> • <a href=\"/Potion_of_attraction\" title=\"Potion of attraction\">Attraction</a> • <a href=\"/Potion_of_berserk_rage\" title=\"Potion of berserk rage\">Berserk rage</a> • <a href=\"/Potion_of_brilliance\" title=\"Potion of brilliance\">Brilliance</a> • <a href=\"/Potion_of_cancellation\" title=\"Potion of cancellation\">Cancellation</a> • <a href=\"/Potion_of_curing\" title=\"Potion of curing\">Curing</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Degeneration</a> • <a href=\"/Potion_of_enlightenment\" title=\"Potion of enlightenment\">Enlightenment</a> • <a href=\"/Potion_of_experience\" title=\"