 with that liquid!}}\n\n==History==\n*Prior to [[0.18]], the potion lowered a random stat by 1-4 instead of decreasing every stat by 1-3.\n*Prior to [[0.13]], having a stat reduced to 0 could cause [[stat death]]. This was replaced by the [[stat zero]] penalties.\n\n{{potions}}"}